My Baby, My Heart, My Everything

To Amira, the Love of My Life

My heart belongs only to you, my baby. To me, you are not just important, you are my entire world. Every thought I have carries your name, every dream I see has your face.

My heart waits for you, not with doubt, but with certainty. Even if the whole world turns against you, I stand beside you without hesitation. Just one word from you, and I will cross oceans to reach you.

Amira, you are the peace I pray for, the answer to every question my heart asks. When I say forever, I mean it with everything I am.

My promise is not just words; it is a commitment written in my soul.
